title: Swanshurst School
data: Swanshurst School is a secondary school and sixth form for girls aged 11 to 19 years, located in Birmingham,England.[1] It is a community school administered by Birmingham City Council.[2] Swanshurst offers GCSEs and BTECs as programmes of study for pupils, while students in the sixth form have the option to study from a range of A-Levels and further BTECs.[3] This West Midlands school or sixth form college related article is a stub.
